📧 Email Template - UI/UX Design
Welcome to the GitHub repository for my Email Template project, created as part of my UI/UX Design internship at Codsoft. This project focuses on designing a clean, responsive, and user-friendly email template that can be used for various communication purposes.

🌟 Features
Responsive Design: The template is designed to look great on all devices, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones.
Clean Layout: A minimalistic and professional design that ensures the content is easy to read and visually appealing.
Customizable: Easily adaptable for different purposes, such as newsletters, marketing campaigns, or transactional emails.
Cross-Platform Compatibility: Tested across multiple email clients to ensure consistent appearance and functionality.
🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Responsive Media Queries
📂 Project Structure
bash
Copy code
